<span id="freeTextContainer204557154803440099">After spending his career handling high profile legal cases, author Mark M Bello now provides readers a close-up view of the social justice battlefront. Each book in the Zachary Blake Betrayal Series is a ripped from the headlines novel inspired by not only Bello’s legal experiences, but his concern for our current sociopolitical landscape.<br/><br/>After having had the pleasure of reading all 6 books in the Zachary Blake legal series I can say in my opinion that the authors talent increases with each new</span>
  <span id="freeText204557154803440099" style="display:none">After spending his career handling high profile legal cases, author Mark M Bello now provides readers a close-up view of the social justice battlefront. Each book in the Zachary Blake Betrayal Series is a ripped from the headlines novel inspired by not only Bello’s legal experiences, but his concern for our current sociopolitical landscape.<br /><br />After having had the pleasure of reading all 6 books in the Zachary Blake legal series I can say in my opinion that the authors talent increases with each new addition to the series, Supreme Betrayal is the latest in the series and is the story of a woman (Hayley Larson) that is still haunted by a sexual assault that took place over 20 years ago, she now faces the sexual predator (Oliver Wilkinson) who is the President’s nominee for a vacant seat on the Supreme Court, Hayley is determined to prevent this man from gaining that position and with the help attorney Zachary Blake the fight begins.<br /><br />Expertly written the author captures the true essence of the characters bringing them to life ensuring the reader gets maximum enjoyment. Highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="204557154803440099" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

