<span id="freeTextContainer11901327986404677978">Supreme Betrayal gives a voice and story behind the struggles victims of sexual assault face when Attorney Zachary Blake takes a high-profile case. The cards are stacked against Hayley Larson, but that is when Blake does his miracles. Things get dirty and discouraging, almost losing hope. I am always amazed at Mark M. Bello&apos;s ability to place the reader in the victim&apos;s shoes; you feel their fear, shame, and disbelief. Then you get that glimmer of hope... <br/><br/>Mark M. Bello thrives, relishes, and exce</span>
  <span id="freeText11901327986404677978" style="display:none">Supreme Betrayal gives a voice and story behind the struggles victims of sexual assault face when Attorney Zachary Blake takes a high-profile case. The cards are stacked against Hayley Larson, but that is when Blake does his miracles. Things get dirty and discouraging, almost losing hope. I am always amazed at Mark M. Bello's ability to place the reader in the victim's shoes; you feel their fear, shame, and disbelief. Then you get that glimmer of hope... <br /><br />Mark M. Bello thrives, relishes, and excels at writing controversial and emotional topics. Supreme Betrayal is the sixth book in the Zachary Blake Legal thrillers and throws you in the fire from the very beginning. Using a fictional character, Attorney Zachary Blake, the author defends victims in criminal courts. Each novel has turmoil and tragedy, growth, and a measure of victory. This author is premier in legal thrillers and his character is a force to be reckoned with. </span>
